channel.title: Help getting server up
channel.description: Like the title says, I need help getting my server up. I tried port forwarding but my parents changed the username and password on the router and they won't tell me it. So then i found out about the uTorrent method, which seemed to work like a charm. But when I checked my server status with a status checker, it said my server is down. I made sure my uTorrent is set at port 43594, I ran my server before opening uTorrent, and I opened port 43594 on my computer. Any help would be appreciated, since I just spent the last half year of my life coding my server, and I would be pretty mad if I can't get it up.
